# Per-project one-off scripts (not imported by the algorithm).
#
# Typical contents: `refresh_<name>.py` — fetches a snapshot from an external
# API and writes the result into `../data/<name>.csv`. Run manually whenever
# you want a fresher bundled snapshot.
#
# These scripts MUST NOT be imported by main.py or any model — the algorithm
# reads bundled data from `../data/` via plain disk I/O.
#
# Pair with `data/<name>.csv`.
